OL,3,CFamily fundraising for cooling cots to
OL,4,Cgive mothers more time with babies
OL,6,F"We didn't want to see him at first.
OL,7,FAnd then as soon as he was born, that
OL,8,Fwas it. We just became obsessed with
OL,9,Fthis beautiful, perfect baby that just
OL,10,Funfortunately, was no longer alive,"
OL,11,Fsaid Chelsea.
OL,13,F"We were processing all these
OL,14,Femotions, not really knowing how to
OL,15,Fnavigate this time, you know, how best
OL,16,Fto look after him. Would we be able to
OL,17,Fbathe him? Would we get to dress him?
OL,18,FWould we actually get to spend any
OL,19,Ftime with him? Would our family get to
OL,20,Fmeet him? Would our children, you
OL,21,Fknow, get to meet him?
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
