OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F351A1769000529
OL,3,CFamily fundraising for cooling cots to
OL,4,Cgive mothers more time with babies
OL,6,F"There were so many questions that we
OL,7,Fwere trying to process and grieve
OL,8,Fourselves and our children to be able
OL,9,Fto grieve, too."
OL,11,FThe hospital had a cooling cot and a
OL,12,Fsmaller scale cuddle cot so they could
OL,13,Fbring their baby home.
OL,15,FWhat is a cooling cot?
OL,17,FA cooling cot has a system that
OL,18,Fcirculates chilled water through a
OL,19,Fthin pad that can be wrapped around
OL,20,Fthe baby, or placed under a mattress
OL,21,Fin a cot or Moses basket.
