OL,4,Cgive mothers more time with babies
OL,6,FThe system allows gentle cooling and
OL,7,Fhelps to preserve the baby's
OL,8,Fappearance after death.
OL,10,FChelsea says that without it, her
OL,11,Ffamily would only have 2 or 3 hours
OL,12,Fwith Romeo before he would have to go
OL,13,Fto the hospital mortuary.
OL,15,F"The ten days that we had with Romeo,
OL,16,Fthere's absolutely no doubt that we
OL,17,Fwould not be the people we are now. We
OL,18,Fhad time to grieve. We had time to
OL,19,Fprocess," said Chelsea.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
