OL,3,CFamily fundraising for cooling cots to
OL,4,Cgive mothers more time with babies
OL,6,F"We had time to accept what happened,
OL,7,Fand we had time to really deal with
OL,8,Four emotions and our feelings, with
OL,9,FRomeo. And just to leave the hospital
OL,10,Fwith him just felt right.
OL,12,F"The idea of him being in the hospital
OL,13,Fmortuary and literally walking out the
OL,14,Fdoors of that hospital with an empty
OL,15,Fcar seat and getting into a car and
OL,16,Fdriving an hour home back to Kendal
OL,17,Ffrom Barrow was just an unbearable
OL,18,Fthought," she added.
