OL,4,Cgive mothers more time with babies
OL,6,FAround 1 in every 250 births in
OL,7,FEngland is a stillbirth, according to
OL,8,Fthe NHS.
OL,10,FChelsea and her family want to help
OL,11,Fothers who are experiencing a similar
OL,12,Fthing to what they went through.
OL,14,FThey started the charity 'Remembering
OL,15,FRomeo' and so far they have raised
OL,16,Fseventeen thousand pounds for 5
OL,17,Fcooling cots in and around Cumbria.
OL,19,F"There are hospitals that do exist in
OL,20,Fthe UK that don't have a single one of
OL,21,Fthese cooling cots," said Chelsea.
