OL,3,CFamily fundraising for cooling cots to
OL,4,Cgive mothers more time with babies
OL,6,F"The one at Barrow was really
OL,7,Fimportant for us because we were just
OL,8,Fso blessed that actually we had such a
OL,9,Fpositive experience in such a
OL,10,Ftraumatic circumstance.
OL,12,F"The idea that somebody else might
OL,13,Fhave needed the cooling cot when we
OL,14,Fwere using it, you know, what if we're
OL,15,Ftaking this other family's time away?
OL,16,FWhat if the cooling cot broke? Twins?"
OL,18,FChelsea says she hopes to expand the
OL,19,Fcharity and provide other services
OL,20,Fsuch as counselling.
